{"body": "Where two or more of paragraphs 2 to 5 apply in any particular case the overall maximum sum which falls to be disregarded in that case under those paragraphs is restricted to\u2014\n\u00a325 in the case of a lone parent;\n\u00a320 in any other case.", "citation_label": "UKSI 2012/2885 Sch. 4 para. 1", "citation_path": "uk/regulation/uksi/2012/2885/schedule/4/paragraph/1", "document_class": "regulation", "expression_date": "2026-07-13", "heading": "Schedule 4 paragraph 1", "id": "2cc5573b-4e20-58bf-9fe6-bbe9c425e89c", "identifiers": {"legislation.gov.uk:number": "2885", "legislation.gov.uk:provision": "schedule/4/paragraph/1", "legislation.gov.uk:type": "uksi", "legislation.gov.uk:year": "2012"}, "jurisdiction": "uk", "kind": "paragraph", "language": "en", "legal_identifier": "UKSI 2012/2885 Sch. 4 para. 1", "level": 2, "metadata": {"extent": ["E", "W"], "references_to": ["uksi/2012/2885", "ukia/2012/413"], "retrieved_at": null, "schedule": "4"}, "ordinal": 1, "source_as_of": "2026-07-13", "source_document_id": "uksi/2012/2885", "source_format": "legislation.gov.uk-clml", "source_id": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2012/2885/schedule/4/paragraph/1", "source_path": "sources/uk/regulation/2026-07-13-uk-ctr-enp-disregards/uksi/2012/2885/schedule-4-paragraph-1.xml", "source_url": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2012/2885/schedule/4/paragraph/1", "version": "2026-07-13-uk-ctr-enp-disregards"}
{"body": "In a case where an applicant is a lone parent, \u00a325 of earnings.", "citation_label": "UKSI 2012/2885 Sch. 4 para. 2", "citation_path": "uk/regulation/uksi/2012/2885/schedule/4/paragraph/2", "document_class": "regulation", "expression_date": "2026-07-13", "heading": "Schedule 4 paragraph 2", "id": "e350a15f-8578-5b3d-ad19-3bbd1bd65f45", "identifiers": {"legislation.gov.uk:number": "2885", "legislation.gov.uk:provision": "schedule/4/paragraph/2", "legislation.gov.uk:type": "uksi", "legislation.gov.uk:year": "2012"}, "jurisdiction": "uk", "kind": "paragraph", "language": "en", "legal_identifier": "UKSI 2012/2885 Sch. 4 para. 2", "level": 2, "metadata": {"extent": ["E", "W"], "references_to": ["uksi/2012/2885", "ukia/2012/413"], "retrieved_at": null, "schedule": "4"}, "ordinal": 2, "source_as_of": "2026-07-13", "source_document_id": "uksi/2012/2885", "source_format": "legislation.gov.uk-clml", "source_id": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2012/2885/schedule/4/paragraph/2", "source_path": "sources/uk/regulation/2026-07-13-uk-ctr-enp-disregards/uksi/2012/2885/schedule-4-paragraph-2.xml", "source_url": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2012/2885/schedule/4/paragraph/2", "version": "2026-07-13-uk-ctr-enp-disregards"}
{"body": "If the applicant or, if he has a partner, his partner is a carer, or both are carers, \u00a320 of any earnings received from his or their employment.\nWhere the carer premium is awarded in respect of the applicant and of any partner of his, their earnings must for the purposes of this paragraph be aggregated, but the amount to be disregarded in accordance with sub-paragraph (1) must not exceed \u00a320 of the aggregated amount.\nIn this paragraph the applicant or his partner is a carer if paragraph 9 of Part 3 of Schedule 2 (amount applicable for carers) is satisfied in respect of him.", "citation_label": "UKSI 2012/2885 Sch. 4 para. 4", "citation_path": "uk/regulation/uksi/2012/2885/schedule/4/paragraph/4", "document_class": "regulation", "expression_date": "2026-07-13", "heading": "Schedule 4 paragraph 4", "id": "564e421b-d81f-5364-9d9d-a8f5d00fc5b9", "identifiers": {"legislation.gov.uk:number": "2885", "legislation.gov.uk:provision": "schedule/4/paragraph/4", "legislation.gov.uk:type": "uksi", "legislation.gov.uk:year": "2012"}, "jurisdiction": "uk", "kind": "paragraph", "language": "en", "legal_identifier": "UKSI 2012/2885 Sch. 4 para. 4", "level": 2, "metadata": {"extent": ["E", "W"], "references_to": ["uksi/2012/2885", "ukia/2012/413"], "retrieved_at": null, "schedule": "4"}, "ordinal": 4, "source_as_of": "2026-07-13", "source_document_id": "uksi/2012/2885", "source_format": "legislation.gov.uk-clml", "source_id": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2012/2885/schedule/4/paragraph/4", "source_path": "sources/uk/regulation/2026-07-13-uk-ctr-enp-disregards/uksi/2012/2885/schedule-4-paragraph-4.xml", "source_url": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2012/2885/schedule/4/paragraph/4", "version": "2026-07-13-uk-ctr-enp-disregards"}
{"body": "Any earnings, other than earnings referred to in paragraph 17(9)(b) of Schedule 1, derived from employment which ended before the day in respect of which the applicant first satisfies the conditions for entitlement to a reduction under an authority\u2019s scheme.", "citation_label": "UKSI 2012/2885 Sch. 4 para. 9", "citation_path": "uk/regulation/uksi/2012/2885/schedule/4/paragraph/9", "document_class": "regulation", "expression_date": "2026-07-13", "heading": "Schedule 4 paragraph 9", "id": "d14cdbc9-1632-50fb-a407-97337ee3a03d", "identifiers": {"legislation.gov.uk:number": "2885", "legislation.gov.uk:provision": "schedule/4/paragraph/9", "legislation.gov.uk:type": "uksi", "legislation.gov.uk:year": "2012"}, "jurisdiction": "uk", "kind": "paragraph", "language": "en", "legal_identifier": "UKSI 2012/2885 Sch. 4 para. 9", "level": 2, "metadata": {"extent": ["E", "W"], "references_to": ["uksi/2012/2885", "ukia/2012/413"], "retrieved_at": null, "schedule": "4"}, "ordinal": 9, "source_as_of": "2026-07-13", "source_document_id": "uksi/2012/2885", "source_format": "legislation.gov.uk-clml", "source_id": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2012/2885/schedule/4/paragraph/9", "source_path": "sources/uk/regulation/2026-07-13-uk-ctr-enp-disregards/uksi/2012/2885/schedule-4-paragraph-9.xml", "source_url": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2012/2885/schedule/4/paragraph/9", "version": "2026-07-13-uk-ctr-enp-disregards"}
